The Sugar Bowl has sit-down service with diner food, but we just grabbed sweet treats from the counter to go.
It's very ... pink ... on the inside as well.
I'm no girly-girl, but I could get down with this in some contexts--even this context--but the modern updates to the décor made it come off a bit too much like a little girl's bedroom for my taste.
