It was easy to tell the locals from the tourists as a dust storm blew in.
The place practically cleared out with cameras clicking and videos rolling to capture this common local event.
At some point they filtered back in to finish their half melted ice cream treats.
I have to say as a local I will only return with out of towners who appreciate the novelty of the place.
It is just your average ice cream shop.

